Name: Robots: create AI
About the game: 《Robots: create AI》is a puzzle programming game. Maps of game will change randomly, sometimes the start lands are also random, then will appear different ways to the destinations. Write programs for robots with picture programming langue, make robots can get to the destinations whatever how maps and start lands changed.
